的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=8BFF\" target=\"_blank\">U+8BFF</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-8BFF\"></p>\n          <p><b>Main pronunciation 主要发音:</b> w&#x11B;i</p>\n          <p><b>Other pronunciations 其它发音:</b> Not exists.</p>\n          <p><b>Original meaning 本义:</b> Meaning lay blame on others.</p>\n          <p><b>English senses 英语理解:</b></p>\n          <p><b>Usage example 用法举例:</b> &#x63A8;&#x8AC9; tu&#x12B; w&#x11B;i (prevarication)</p>\n          <p><b>Importance by frequency 常用频率:</b></p>\n          <p><b>Shuowen 说文解字:</b> &#x7E8D;&#x4E5F;&#x5F9E;&#x8A00;&#x59D4;&#x8072;</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Character decomposition 字形分解 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br>Compound &#x8AC9; &#xD;&#xA;from mouth-speak (&#x8BA0;)&#x8A01; y&#xE1;n and &#xD;&#xA;phonetic appoint &#x59D4; w&#x11B;i &#xD;&#xA;simp &#x8BFF;.</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Decomposition notes 字形分解说明 <a href=\"https://dixin.github.io/Etymology/decomposition-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Simplification rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Simplification rule explained <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Variant rule :</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Variant rule clarification <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Applied rules <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b> R01 &#x8BA0;&#x8A01;&#x8A00;</p>\n          <p><b>New font rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p><a target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-1 bg-primary col-md-9 col-sm-8 etymology-result\" id=\"etymologyCharacters\">\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known oracle characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known bronze characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span> Seal characters (1)</h3>\n        <ul class=\"list-inline list-unstyled\">\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-S01736.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>诿</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>诿<br>（諉）<br>wěi<br>推托，把责任推给别人：诿说。推诿。诿托。诿过于人。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诿</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［wěi］<br>［《廣韻》女恚切，去寘，娘。］<br>“诿1”的繁体字。<br>(1)烦重。<br>(2)连累；委托。<br>(3)推托；推委。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诿</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【酉集上】【言字部】　諉； 康熙笔画：15； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/1188.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页1188第18</span></a><br>【唐韻】【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】?女恚切，音㨅。【說文】纍也。諈諉，見上諈字註。【前漢·胡建傳】執事不諉上。【師古註】累也。言執事者當見法卽行，不可以事累於上也。【唐書·岑羲傳】羲誠材，何諉之拘。【音義】累也。　又託也。【前漢·賈誼傳】尚有可諉者。【蔡謨曰】諉，託也。【正韻牋】諉，猶委也。言尚可他委。後人因借爲推諉、諉謝字用。　又【集韻】邕危切，音逶。爾雅：諈諉，累也。謝嶠讀。　又【集韻】弋睡切，音瓗。又而睡切，音汭。義?同。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诿</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诿</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>本义指累，烦劳。也有推卸的意思。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">Humiliate<br>Basic explanation of words<br>Humiliate<br>(诿)<br>wěi<br>Dodge, transfer the responsibility to others: Hui said. Excuse. Huo Tuo. Blame too much.<br>Humiliate<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［wěi］<br>[\"Guangyun\" female Yun cut, go to set, mother. ]<br>Traditional characters for \"诿1\".<br>(1) Annoying.<br>(2) Involvement; commission.<br>(3) Dodge; Selection Committee.<br>Humiliate<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[You Ji 1] [Words Department] 　诿; Kangxi strokes: 15; Page number: page 1188 18<br>[Tang Yun] [Ji Yun] [Rhyme Meeting] [Positive Rhyme]? Female 恚切, sound 㨅. [Said Wen] Tired too.諈诿, see the note on the character of 諈刈. [Previous Han·Hu Jian Biography] The deacon didn't falter. [Shigu Note] Tired too. The deacon should see the law and do it, and don’t get tired of everything. [Book of Tang·Cenxi Biography] Xi is honest and talented, He Zhuozhi. [Sound meaning] Tired.　Take it again. [Previous Han·Jia Yi Biography] There are still people who can be blamed. [Cai Mo said] Zhuo, please also. [Zheng Yun Jian] Zhuo, still weird. Words are still acceptable. Later generations used the word for excuse and excuse.　[Jiyun] Yong Weiqie, Yin Bei. Erya: I'm tired and tired. Xie Qiao read.　 [Ji Yun] Sleeping and cutting, sound 瓗. Sleeping and cutting again, sound. Righteous? Same.<br>Humiliate<br>Source glyph<br>Humiliate<br>Name meaning<br>The original meaning refers to tired, troublesome. It also means to shirk.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148275901645382.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148275901645382.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148275901645382.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">诿<br>形声字。言(i)表意,篆书形体像开口说话,表示用言语委托以事相累;委(wei)表声,委有托付、任命之义,表示用言<br>语托事于人。形旁简化。本义是带累,麻烦别人。引申为推托、<br>推委。<br>推托;推卸:~过「推~。<br>wěi<br>~过 ~说 推~<br>誘誘<br>诿<br>简<br>liitiil h 出<br>***</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Унизить<br>Пиктофонетические символы.<br>Янь (и) выражает смысл, сценарий печати подобен открытию, чтобы говорить, что означает, что он обременен словесным доверием; вэй выражает свой голос, что означает доверие и назначение, выражение использования слов для доверия людям.<br>Упростите форму.<br>Первоначальное значение - приносить усталость и беспокоить других.<br>Расширение - комитет по уклонению и отбору.<br>Уклонение; уклонение: ~ пас \"толчок ~.<br>~ Over ~ Talk ~<br>Приманка<br>Унизить<br>просто<br>liitiil h out<br>***</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">wěi</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><span class=\"paragraph\">гл.</span></div>\n  <div>1) беспокоить, утруждать, причинять заботы</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">执事不诿上 выполнять дела, не беспокоя начальника (императора)</span></div>\n  <div>2) ссылаться на...; выдумывать предлог, под предлогом...</div>\n  <div>3) поручать, доверять, предоставлять</div>\n  <div>4) слагать с себя ответственность, сваливать вину на другого</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">诿过于人 свалить свою ошибку на другого</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=诿\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=诿&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=诿\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=诿\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=诿\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/诿\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=诿\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/诿\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=诿&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#诿\">Char lookup site</a></p>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"讠","pinyins":["yan2"]},{"glyph":"委","pinyins":["Wei3","wei1","wei3"]}],"isMentionedAt__hanziyuan_without_charactersWithComponent":["諉"]}